item.title: Error?
item.dc:creator: @K0y K0y
item.description:
@K0y wrote:

It looks like you’ve added in a new folder and the file you’re trying to compile is inside that folder.
You need to change the compiler’s compiling parameters… for e.g. -d bin src\server\event\*.java
That sets the event folder as one of the directories for the compiler to parse.
It’s beyond me why that common directory isn’t already in your compiler though…
